    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS variable valve timing. This example is paired with a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M-differential lock for optimal power delivery. The chassis has been properly sorted with a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed bushings, ensuring the MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension maintain factory-spec kinematics. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive valve clearance adjustment and a cooling system overhaul. While the finish shows minor signs of spirited use, the mechanical assembly is tight, offering the linear power band and telepathic steering response that define this generation of M-car.",
