      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and daily reliability. The exterior features a deep, lustrous finish, showing only the expected minor stone chips from highway commuting and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium upholstery is supple with no tears, though the driver\u2019s side bolster shows light entry wear. Every electronic feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the high-fidelity sound system, functions exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts with precision. I have adhered to a strict maintenance schedule, including a recent full synthetic oil change and a brake fluid flush within the last 3,000 miles. The tires have ample tread remaining for many seasons to come. This is a smoke-free, pet-free car with a clean title and a organized folder of service records ready for its next owner.",
